code: export function register(){if(process.env.NODE_ENV==='production'&&'serviceWorker'in navigator){window.addEventListener('load',()=>{const swUrl="".concat(process.env.PUBLIC_URL,"/service-worker.js");navigator.serviceWorker.register(swUrl).then(registration=>{console.log('Service Worker registrado con éxito:',registration);}).catch(error=>{console.error('Error durante el registro del Service Worker:',error);});});}}
